---
/** Value props: co-owned, ad-free, your data, transparent. Vision-aligned. */
---

<section class="section home-features" aria-labelledby="features-heading">
  <div class="app-container">
    <header class="home-features__header">
      <p class="section-eyebrow">Why Reclaim</p>
      <h2 id="features-heading" class="home-features__title">
        A space that answers to you
      </h2>
      <p class="body-text home-features__lead">
        No feeds. No engagement hacks. No surveillance. Just a calm place to think, write, and build tools that serve human will — not ad exchanges.
      </p>
    </header>

    <div class="home-features__grid">
      <article class="card home-features__card card-clickable">
        <div class="home-features__icon" aria-hidden="true">
          <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
            <path d="M17 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-4-4H5a4 4 0 0 0-4 4v2" />
            <circle cx="9" cy="7" r="4" />
            <path d="M23 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-3-3.87M16 3.13a4 4 0 0 1 0 7.75" />
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="section-title home-features__card-title">Co-owned</h3>
        <p class="body-text-small home-features__card-text">
          You’re not a user in someone else’s product. You co-own and co-create your digital space — your ideas, your rules.
        </p>
      </article>

      <article class="card home-features__card card-clickable">
        <div class="home-features__icon" aria-hidden="true">
          <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
            <path d="M12 22s8-4 8-10V5l-8-3-8 3v7c0 6 8 10 8 10z" />
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="section-title home-features__card-title">Ad-free & private</h3>
        <p class="body-text-small home-features__card-text">
          No tracking, no “personalization” that profiles you. Your attention and data stay yours — we don’t sell them.
        </p>
      </article>

      <article class="card home-features__card card-clickable">
        <div class="home-features__icon" aria-hidden="true">
          <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
            <rect x="3" y="11" width="18" height="11" rx="2" ry="2" />
            <path d="M7 11V7a5 5 0 0 1 10 0v4" />
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="section-title home-features__card-title">Your data, your custody</h3>
        <p class="body-text-small home-features__card-text">
          Writing and conversations live in spaces you understand and control — not in black boxes optimized for someone else’s growth.
        </p>
      </article>

      <article class="card home-features__card card-clickable">
        <div class="home-features__icon" aria-hidden="true">
          <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
            <path d="M2 12s3-7 10-7 10 7 10 7-3 7-10 7-10-7-10-7Z" />
            <circle cx="12" cy="12" r="3" />
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="section-title home-features__card-title">Transparent & legible</h3>
        <p class="body-text-small home-features__card-text">
          Simple tools you can explain end to end. No algorithmic mystery — you see how things work and can change them.
        </p>
      </article>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .home-features {
    background: var(--color-surface);
    padding-top: var(--sp-8);
    padding-bottom: var(--sp-8);
  }

  .home-features__header {
    text-align: center;
    max-width: 640px;
    margin: 0 auto var(--sp-7);
  }

  .home-features__title {
    font-size: 2rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    line-height: 1.25;
    color: var(--color-text-primary);
    margin-top: var(--sp-2);
    margin-bottom: var(--sp-3);
  }

  .home-features__lead {
    margin: 0;
  }

  .home-features__grid {
    display: grid;
    gap: var(--sp-5);
    grid-template-columns: 1fr;
  }

  @media (min-width: 640px) {
    .home-features__grid {
      grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
    }
  }

  @media (min-width: 1024px) {
    .home-features__grid {
      grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr);
      gap: var(--sp-4);
    }
  }

  .home-features__card {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    transition: border-color 150ms ease;
  }

  .home-features__icon {
    width: 40px;
    height: 40px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    border-radius: 12px;
    background: var(--color-primary-light);
    color: var(--color-primary);
    margin-bottom: var(--sp-4);
  }

  .home-features__icon svg {
    width: 22px;
    height: 22px;
  }

  .home-features__card-title {
    font-size: 1.125rem;
    margin-bottom: var(--sp-2);
  }

  .home-features__card-text {
    margin: 0;
    flex: 1;
  }
</style>
